data.description: ***Sellers Found Their Dream Home!  Sellers are Motivated!!!    Don't miss out on this Gorgeous Ranch style home in the "Flower Street" Community. This Lovely 3 bedroom/ 2 Bathroom home is a 4 sided Brick home with an inground pool ( 11x 25ft)  and a Big Sunroom with beautiful windows, all on 1 acre of property in a Gorgeous neighborhood. Everyone wants to live here!  The home boasts an Open Floor concept with a Separate Dining room, and two Living Spaces. Feel right at home with the Wood burning stove while curled up watching the Football game. Family room comes with a wall built in- Perfect for a Bar or Pictures. Kitchen has been totally remodeled with Beautiful Soft Close Cabinets , Granite Counters and Under cabinet lighting. All Stainless Steel Appliances with Convey with the sale of the home. New LVP Flooring through.out the home with the exception of the newly tiled floor in the Laundry room.  NO CAPRET! Did I mention that this home has new Champion Windows?  Enjoy the New Water heater, 2 year old HVAC system, 2 year old new Roof, and walk in pantry.  New gutters and new vinyl on the backside of the home all in the last 3 years.  Let's talk about the Master Bathroom!  New tiled shower, new tiled floor, and a new vanity!  Tons of Upgrades!   Don't forget this is a Perfect location for a walk in the morning or after dinner. You can enjoy the playground at Granger park- All within walking distance. Oh, and did I mention that the Whole back yard is fenced in!  $2000 towards closing costs if you use Preferred Lender, Kim Lanius, Statewide Mortgage.
